        <div class="comparison-item">
          <h4>Precedent and Case Law</h4>
          <p>DIFC and ADGM follow binding precedent. References to case law in legal documents need translation that preserves the legal authority being cited.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-item">
          <h4>Equity Principles</h4>
